title: Le Kid & Les Marinellis - Converse Rubber Tracks: Track of the Week
description: The single "La Vie" by Le Kid & Les Marinellis is this week's "Track of the Week". The band entered the studio focused on achieving the exact set-up for each of the five members and recording the vocals, all in French, with a specific sound in mind.
